WORKZONE Office development is an A-grade office campus comprising two, six level buildings totalling approximately 27,962 sqm NLA. 

1 Nash Street has a side core with remote fire stairs at the two corners on the same side as the lift core offering highly efficient office space. The ground floor provides for loading areas and bicycle storage, locker and change room facilities. Large internal court-yard with landscaped gardens for social and relaxation space. Onsite amenities include a cafe.

The top floor (Level 6) is predominantly fitted out to a high specification with 69 workstations, 8 hot desks, 3 offices, 4 meeting rooms, and 1 x 20 seater boardroom, leaving an open plan area at the southern end of the floor which is currently unfitted. The floor provides a brilliant ‘town hall’ meeting opportunity with a large, modern breakout opening up to 12 seater meeting room.
